    "stem": "A 19-year-old college student presents after a generalized tonic-clonic seizure witnessed in the dormitory. MRI is normal; EEG shows generalized spike-and-wave discharges. Phenytoin is prescribed. What is phenytoin's primary anticonvulsant mechanism?",
    "optionA": "Direct bacterial DNA gyrase inhibition independent of disease context",
