    "explanationC": "DNA gyrase inhibition is a bactericidal antibiotic mechanism with no role in cholinergic neurotransmission or dementia management.",
    "explanationD": "IL-5 neutralization targets eosinophilic pathways in asthma — completely unrelated to the cholinergic deficit in Alzheimer's disease.",
