    "stem": "A 70-year-old woman with painful diabetic neuropathy fails gabapentin due to sedation and is switched to a tricyclic antidepressant. What mechanism of TCAs provides neuropathic pain relief independent of antidepressant effects?",
    "optionA": "Skeletal neuromuscular nicotinic agonism as the core therapeutic pathway",
