    "stem": "A 58-year-old woman with newly diagnosed HFrEF (EF 32%) and type 2 diabetes is started on the 'four pillars' of GDMT. What is the mechanism by which beta-blockers (e.g., carvedilol) reduce mortality in heart failure despite being negative inotropes?",
