    "bennerBreakdown": "Understanding autoimmune synovial inflammation control requires tracing the complete pharmacological pathway from drug-receptor interaction to clinical effect and adverse outcomes. In Musculoskeletal, this mechanism-based reasoning guides safe prescribing, monitoring, and patient education."
