    "stem": "A 52-year-old woman with osteoarthritis knee pain takes ibuprofen with significant relief. What is ibuprofen's mechanism of COX inhibition in reducing inflammatory pain?",
    "optionA": "Irreversible COX-1 inhibition as a universal first-line strategy",
    "optionB": "cyclooxygenase-mediated prostaglandin pathway reduction",
