    "stem": "A 48-year-old woman with RA takes celecoxib and has fewer GI side effects than with naproxen. What is the mechanism of COX-2 selective inhibition that reduces GI toxicity while maintaining anti-inflammatory effect?",
    "optionA": "Direct bacterial DNA gyrase inhibition independent of disease context",
